        WEB_SITE=http://sourceforge.net/projects/ump3c/
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
         ENTERED=20081029
           SHORT="a mp3 steganography tool"
cat << EOF
UnderMP3Cover (ump3c) is a mp3 steganography tool. It will allow you to write
and read hidden messages within mp3 files without creating any audible
differences to the mp3. The messages could be a text file, jpg or any other
file depending on the mp3's size.
EOF
